Write 20 random facts about yourself then tag the same amount of people as minutes it takes you to write the facts. If your tagged it's your turn.

1. I cut my left hand index finger on my first day of culinary school.

2. I graduated high school when I was 16.

3. I worked full time at Disney World from the time that I was 16 to the time that I was 22.

4. I have always loved big women and I will always love big women.

5. I have 5 tattoos and I am going to get more.

6. I only have one true blue best friend in the whole entire world.

7. I went to culinary school when I was 18 because I have always wanted to be a chef ever since I was at least 10 years old.

8. I have only had 4 girlfriends in my entire life and I am really in the need of a long term relationship.

9. I don't like going to the doctor because they blame all my problems on my weightno matter what's wrong with me at the time.

10. I have alot of secret sexual fantasies, fantasies that alot of people would consider a little freaky, that I have told to only one person and I know that there is a good chance that i will never get to meet this person.

11. I am in love with a woman I met online and i so want to meet her in person and I am afraid that I will never get to meet her, and it really bothers me because she is so perfect.

12. I love all kinds of movies I watch them all but Star Wars is the best movie series of all time, at least that's what i feel.

13. I listen to all kinds of music from classical to hard rock, from ABBA to ZZ Top and everything in between.

14. I started to listen to rap, hip-hop when I was 18just because my parents hated it, it seemed the more they hated it the more i liked it.

15. I love everything that has to deal with the Southern United States and it's past the Confederacy, Stars and bars, Old Glory, Southern Rock.

16. I have a Confederate battle flag but I am not racistat all I believe in heritage not hate. I am so not racist I dated a black girl for almost a year one time.

17. I like all kinds of food but I am mostly a meat eater I only like a few veggies. My favorite meat is beef and I like it cooked RARE as rare as possible, I have said the bloodier the better.

18. I love women with long hair the longer the better.

19. I want to be a pastry chef eventually and I will have to go back to school for that, I will eventually I just don't have the time or money for that right now.

20. I tend to get depresed when I start to think about how i need a woman in my life, and sometimes I fear that I will never find the right woman for me. When I start to think about that I start to think that I will die cold and alone. But I'm OK right now.

Well the subject says it all I am extremly lonely, and it seems as though I am geeting depressed again. I usually get depressed about every 3 to 4 years this time it's because I am so damn lonely. I mean I am 23 and I have yet to have a serious relationship that could possibly lead to more, I mean I have had relationships but nothing that I would call serious. It's to hard to find a woman that likes all the same things as me, and lives close enough to me to date. I mean I sometimes see myself dying cold, alone, and in the dark with nobody there to love me. I really need to start a serious relationship with somebody soon or else I don't know what will happen to me. I am a nice guy with a lot of love to give to the right woman, but these days it seems the only thing women want is a handsome built guy with an IQ of 3. It seems that most women can't look past my physical appearance to see the true me, I am fat as hell I know that but that's the way I look and I will alwys look that way. I have tried to lose weight but it doesn't work for me. I'm sorry for all the self pity guys I am just really starting to feel depressed anyway I have said enough for now be back later bye.

Well the weekend is here once again 2 in the morning making my entry. I have to open tomorrow at 11:00 A.M. I am gonna be so tired but that's a good thing too that means I am going to be off on Friday night, not like I'm going to be doing anything though. But maybe I can catch somebody online to chat with not everybody is up in the middle of the night like me. I hope I can catch Brandy online I really like talking to her I think we have alot in common anyway one can only hope right. Well I guess I should probably try to get a little sleep I don't think I'm going to get any though. Lately I have had so much on my mind it seems like it gets harder and harder to go to sleep every night, I just worry about my life and the lack of companionship I have in it. Sorry I know I talk about that all the time well I got to try and get some sleep now I'll be back tomorrow night/morning good night all.

Oh my God I am so bored I mean look at the time on this entry. That's right it is almost 2:30 in the morning and here I am sitting on the computer wishing there was someone online that I could talk to. God this insomnia is killing me I swear one of these days I am gonna figure out how to get rid of my insomnia. I mean there is only so many things you can watch on tv at this time of night am I right? But even though I complain about it sometimes I still like it I mean I can say that I can go longer than most people without sleeping. Besides that alot of good things can happen at night if you know what I mean (wink wink). Well I don't really have to go but I can't think of anything else to write about so I guess I'll talk to you later bye for now.

Well as we all know the price of gas is going up AGAIN! Like it really needs to it's already high enough as it is. I really don't see how they expect people to make it in this world they need to pay us more this is ridiculous. Anyhow other than me freaking out about gas prices I have to work again all weekend and all week. So looks like last weekend was my only fun for quite sometime. Like I said before my life is so boring I really need something to happen to me to spice up my life. Like maybe get a girlfriend that would really spice up my life, but you all are probably getting tired of hearing me say that. Well I got to go now so I guess I'll talk to you later bye for now.

Well I haven't made an entry in a couple of days so here's how I'm doing. Friday in Ybor City with ny friend was awesome great city nothing but bars, clubs, pizza places, and drunk college students as far as the eye can see. My friend got so drunk he couldn't even drive so I had to drive back, that was interesting only because he drives an automatic and I drive a standard. I kept on trying to push on the clutch so I could shift it was actually pretty funny. On Thursday when I took my friend out for his 21st birthday boy did we both get drunk, we was of course drinking beer. But we also had 2 liquid cocaines, and 2 Irish carbombs, and I don't know how much beer, so yeah I was felling really happy. I had to work yesterday but today is my day off I am not doing a damn thing today staying at home on the computer or sleeping. At least tonight I get to see the new episode of Iron Chef America that will be great well I don't really have to go, but I am writing too much here so I will say good bye for now.

Well even though I screwed up the other day and I am still wishing for another chance to do it right this week might be OK. One of my friends is turning 21 on Tuesday so I will have to take him out and really get him plastered not to sound gay that's just what you do to your friends when they turn 21. I am also supposed to go to Ebor City with another one of my friends on Friday strip clubs and booze as far as the eye can see, sound like fun huh. Anyway other than that just work, work, and more work. But I think I will have some fun this week which is a good thing cause I don't get to go out and party with my friends as much as I would like too. They are either too young to go drinking or they are married and don't want a single person hanging out with them. Well got to go be back tomorrow night bye for now.

Well I guess all hope cannot be discarded yet. Don't get me wrong I did screw up yesterday, but I think if I am hopefull enough amazing girl will give me another chance. If she does I would love for some of you people out there to give me some date advice. I know it sounds stupid a 23 year old asking for dating advice, but I really haven't been out on that many dates. And I haven't been on one period for about 4 or 5 years now, so any advice would be greatly apperciated. Well got to go now talk to you later bye for now.

Well everybody I do belive I have royally screwed up today. Today I finally met the amazing girl I have been talking about. And yes she was amazingly beautiful just like I thought, but like the loser that I am I choked. And by choked I mean that if she never wanted to talk to me again I would understand. The whole time I was in her presence I don't belive I said more than 50 words out loud, I didn't even tell her how beautiful she looked. It's not like I didn't want to talk to her it's just for some stupid reason I couldn't get my mouth to say the words I wanted to say. That's the story of my life Eli the screw up. I am going to die alone in this world I know I am. It's funny just about the only thing I want in this life is to have a serious relationship with somebody, and I can't even do that right. I finally meet somebody I really like and I BLOW IT. well I'm pretty sure that whatever I could've had with this woman is over unless she tells me other words. Well I got to go now I guess I'll be back later.

Well today is the big day I finally get to meet the amazing girl I wrote about the other day by the way that's what I'm going to call her from now on. I'm going to meet her at an art museum I am so nervous I sure hope I don't mess anything up. I also hope I can make a good enough impression on her that we could possibly see a little more of each other. I think she looks fantastic I haven't seen her body yet just her face, but if her face is any preview to what her body will look like woo watch out boys. But to be truthfull I could care less what she looks like, looks are just a bonus I like her for her mind and the way she thinks, like they say beauty is only skin deep. I believe she has a very good out look on life and the way we should all treat each other. Well I got to go now wish me luck tody everybody I'll make sure I write about the day when I get home tomorrow.

I think I will be going out to an art museum on Saturday with the girl of my dreams. That is if I get Saturday off I really hope I do. I can't wait to meet this woman in person. If she is as amazing in person as she is on-line than this is going to be fantastic. I still can't believe I have met this woman sounds like my luck is starting to change for the good. All I can say is it's about time.

I think I have just met the girl of my dreams. She is amazing, she is everything I have ever dreamed of. I can't believe I have met a girl that likes so many of the same things I like. She even has the same ideals about marriage and families that I do. I love the way she looks at the world and how she feels about the roles of women and men. There is a slight age difference but that means nothing to me. I cannot stop thinking about her, I know that this serious because I just chated with her for almost 10 hours, and I cannot chat with someone that long if I didn't like or if we didn't have anything in common. I think if everything goes right with this woman I could really fall in love with her. My life could be gaining alot more meaning here pretty soon.
